{
  "video_id": "UT_nWVLi4Ws",
  "title": "Sadhguru on Marriage – Choosing Consciously",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6580.0,
      "end_time": 8346.0,
      "text": "Questioner: My name is Ananth."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 8346.0,
      "end_time": 11476.0,
      "text": "My question is about marriage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11476.0,
      "end_time": 12816.0,
      "text": "divorce."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 12816.0,
      "end_time": 13740.0,
      "text": "I’m married"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13740.0,
      "end_time": 15112.0,
      "text": "Sadhguru: No, no, they are two different things (Laughter & Applause)."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15112.0,
      "end_time": 18804.0,
      "text": "Questioner: …marriage"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18804.0,
      "end_time": 20555.0,
      "text": "what I see today is"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20555.0,
      "end_time": 22833.0,
      "text": "many youngsters like"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22833.0,
      "end_time": 25074.0,
      "text": "many of them they don’t want to marry"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25074.0,
      "end_time": 27638.0,
      "text": "and few of them who marry"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 27638.0,
      "end_time": 32484.0,
      "text": "there are occasions where they are getting divorced;"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32484.0,
      "end_time": 37495.0,
      "text": "so would you like to throw some light on this situation Sadhguru?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 37495.0,
      "end_time": 43643.0,
      "text": "Sadhguru: See, you need to understand the institution of marriage."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43643.0,
      "end_time": 46686.0,
      "text": "it’s about bringing a certain sanctity"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46686.0,
      "end_time": 50268.0,
      "text": "to the simple basic needs that every human being has."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50268.0,
      "end_time": 51652.0,
      "text": "there are physical needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51652.0,
      "end_time": 53194.0,
      "text": "there are psychological needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53194.0,
      "end_time": 54515.0,
      "text": "there are economic needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54515.0,
      "end_time": 55492.0,
      "text": "emotional needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 55492.0,
      "end_time": 56404.0,
      "text": "social needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56404.0,
      "end_time": 58991.0,
      "text": "variety of needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 58991.0,
      "end_time": 63074.0,
      "text": "To fulfill all these things we set up an institution called marriage"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63074.0,
      "end_time": 66172.0,
      "text": "where all these can be conducted in a sensible manner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66172.0,
      "end_time": 70802.0,
      "text": "otherwise if we did it on the streets like every other creature"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70802.0,
      "end_time": 72342.0,
      "text": "it would turn ugly for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72342.0,
      "end_time": 76314.0,
      "text": "And we will feel not good about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76314.0,
      "end_time": 79074.0,
      "text": "So,to bring some sense of organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79074.0,
      "end_time": 80498.0,
      "text": "some aesthetic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80498.0,
      "end_time": 81633.0,
      "text": "some stability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81633.0,
      "end_time": 87814.0,
      "text": "because man and woman coming together naturally brought fresh life."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87814.0,
      "end_time": 88464.0,
      "text": "it is..."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88464.0,
      "end_time": 90234.0,
      "text": "compared to any other creature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90234.0,
      "end_time": 92692.0,
      "text": "it is the most helpless life"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92692.0,
      "end_time": 95046.0,
      "text": "which needs maximum amount of support."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95046.0,
      "end_time": 97833.0,
      "text": "You could leave a puppy on the street;"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97833.0,
      "end_time": 100752.0,
      "text": "as long as he gets food, he grows up into a good dog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 100752.0,
      "end_time": 102515.0,
      "text": "no problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 102515.0,
      "end_time": 104284.0,
      "text": "But not so with a human being;"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104284.0,
      "end_time": 106542.0,
      "text": "he doesn’t need just physical support,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106542.0,
      "end_time": 109072.0,
      "text": "he needs variety of support and"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 109072.0,
      "end_time": 111633.0,
      "text": "above all the stable situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 111633.0,
      "end_time": 115872.0,
      "text": "Whether there should be marriage in society or not"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115872.0,
      "end_time": 119103.0,
      "text": "one will debate when they are eighteen"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119103.0,
      "end_time": 122984.0,
      "text": "because physical body is asking for freedom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 122984.0,
      "end_time": 124405.0,
      "text": "all right."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 124405.0,
      "end_time": 126632.0,
      "text": "At that time everybody questions –"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 126632.0,
      "end_time": 128572.0,
      "text": "is marriage really needed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 128572.0,
      "end_time": 131993.0,
      "text": "why can’t we just live whichever way we want?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 131993.0,
      "end_time": 134362.0,
      "text": "But when you are three years of age"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134362.0,
      "end_time": 137152.0,
      "text": "you valued marriage immensely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 137152.0,
      "end_time": 139115.0,
      "text": "a stable marriage immensely."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 139115.0,
      "end_time": 140644.0,
      "text": "Isn’t it so?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140644.0,
      "end_time": 141503.0,
      "text": "Yes or no?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 141503.0,
      "end_time": 141885.0,
      "text": "Juhi Chawla: Yes, yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 141885.0,
      "end_time": 145142.0,
      "text": "again when you become forty-five, fifty you’re hundred percent for marriage"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145142.0,
      "end_time": 150883.0,
      "text": "between and eighteen and thirty-five you’re questioning the whole process (Laughter & Applause),"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150883.0,
      "end_time": 151447.0,
      "text": "okay?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 151447.0,
      "end_time": 152934.0,
      "text": "Juhi Chawla: That’s true (Laughs)."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 152934.0,
      "end_time": 156265.0,
      "text": "Sadhguru: Because where the physical body is dominant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156265.0,
      "end_time": 159507.0,
      "text": "at that time if you give in to that"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 159507.0,
      "end_time": 162045.0,
      "text": "then it will question every institution."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 162045.0,
      "end_time": 165904.0,
      "text": "this is hormone fired freedom okay (Laughter)."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 165904.0,
      "end_time": 168543.0,
      "text": "Your intelligence has been hijacked by hormones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168543.0,
      "end_time": 172132.0,
      "text": "so you question the fundamentals of everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 172132.0,
      "end_time": 174863.0,
      "text": "I’m not saying marriage is the thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 174863.0,
      "end_time": 178424.0,
      "text": "but do you have a better alternative?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 178424.0,
      "end_time": 181622.0,
      "text": "If you have a better alternative, damn the marriage"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 181622.0,
      "end_time": 185104.0,
      "text": "but you have not come up with a better alternative"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 185104.0,
      "end_time": 188722.0,
      "text": "because a stable situation is a must for a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 188722.0,
      "end_time": 191332.0,
      "text": "Once you have a child it’s a twenty year project (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 191332.0,
      "end_time": 193283.0,
      "text": "Your whims and fancies will change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 193283.0,
      "end_time": 194494.0,
      "text": "your emotions will change;"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 194494.0,
      "end_time": 198528.0,
      "text": "if that is what it is, don’t get into such situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 198528.0,
      "end_time": 201302.0,
      "text": "It’s not compulsory for everybody to get married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 201302.0,
      "end_time": 202292.0,
      "text": "it’s good young"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 202292.0,
      "end_time": 203903.0,
      "text": "you were saying people are thinking whether to get married."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 203903.0,
      "end_time": 207154.0,
      "text": "I’m glad it is not necessary for everybody"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 207154.0,
      "end_time": 209106.0,
      "text": "but if you get into it and if you"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 209106.0,
      "end_time": 211393.0,
      "text": "especially if you get into children you must understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 211393.0,
      "end_time": 213705.0,
      "text": "it’s a minimum twenty year project"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 213705.0,
      "end_time": 215712.0,
      "text": "whether you like it or you don’t like it."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 215712.0,
      "end_time": 218622.0,
      "text": "Otherwise you shouldn’t get into those projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 218622.0,
      "end_time": 222046.0,
      "text": "you don’t walk into a project, drop it half way and walk away, isn’t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 222046.0,
      "end_time": 223135.0,
      "text": "Juhi Chawla: Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 223135.0,
      "end_time": 224182.0,
      "text": "It’s your choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 224182.0,
      "end_time": 226222.0,
      "text": "but at least choose consciously."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 226222.0,
      "end_time": 228468.0,
      "text": "You don’t have to get married because everybody is getting married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 228468.0,
      "end_time": 232164.0,
      "text": "you don’t have to talk about marriage and divorce in same breath"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 232164.0,
      "end_time": 234904.0,
      "text": "as if they come together (Laughter)."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 234904.0,
      "end_time": 237773.0,
      "text": "This is a completely an American idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 237773.0,
      "end_time": 240193.0,
      "text": "you’re thinking of marriage and divorce together"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 240193.0,
      "end_time": 243312.0,
      "text": "nobody thought of divorce in this country till recently, isn’t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 243312.0,
      "end_time": 244363.0,
      "text": "Juhi Chawla: Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 244363.0,
      "end_time": 246045.0,
      "text": "Sadhguru: So, if it happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 246045.0,
      "end_time": 248015.0,
      "text": "if something happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 248015.0,
      "end_time": 250484.0,
      "text": "something truly went wrong between two people"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 250484.0,
      "end_time": 253545.0,
      "text": "and they have to separate that will any way inevitably happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 253545.0,
      "end_time": 257586.0,
      "text": "You don’t have to plan it at the time of wedding (Laughter)."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 257586.0,
      "end_time": 261882.0,
      "text": "why should you ever talk about marriage and divorce in one breath?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 261882.0,
      "end_time": 263412.0,
      "text": "It's a crime"
    }
  ]
}